OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,FDonald Trump has said a peace deal
OL,7,Fbetween the US and Iran "is now
OL,8,Fcomplete" and will be followed by the
OL,9,Fopening of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FIn a statement on his Truth Social
OL,12,Fplatform at around 10.30pm UK time,
OL,13,Fthe US President said:
OL,14,F"Congratulations to all!
OL,16,F"I hereby fully authorize the toll
OL,17,Ffree opening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,18,Fand, simultaneously herewith,
OL,19,Fauthorize the immediate removal of the
OL,20,FUnited States Naval blockade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
