OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781525476
OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,F"Ships of the World, start your
OL,7,Fengines. Let the oil flow! President
OL,8,FDONALD J. TRUMP."
OL,10,FHowever, a statement by the president
OL,11,Fof Pakistan, which has been acting as
OL,12,Fa key mediator in the peace process,
OL,13,Fsuggested that while terms have been
OL,14,Fagreed, a deal won't be signed until
OL,15,Flate next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
