OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781525476
OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,F"Following intensive talks, we are
OL,7,Fpleased to announce that the Peace
OL,8,FDeal between the United States of
OL,9,FAmerica and Islamic Republic of Iran
OL,10,Fhas been REACHED," Pakistan's prime
OL,11,Fminister Shehbaz Sharif posted on X at
OL,12,F10.15pm UK time.
OL,14,F"Both sides have declared the
OL,15,Fimmediate and permanent termination of
OL,16,Fmilitary operations on all fronts,
OL,17,Fincluding in Lebanon. The official
OL,18,Fsigning ceremony will be on Friday, 19
OL,19,FJune in Switzerland."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
