OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781525476
OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,FSharif thanked the US and Iran for
OL,7,Ftheir "commitment to finding a
OL,8,Fdiplomatic solution to the conflict"
OL,9,Fand expressed his appreciation to
OL,10,FQatar, Saudi Arabia and Turkey for
OL,11,Ftheir contributions to the peace
OL,12,Fprocess.
OL,14,F"With the agreement now in place,
OL,15,Fmediators will facilitate a series of
OL,16,Fmeetings this week," he added.
OL,18,F"These pre-implementation discussions
OL,19,Fwill lay the foundation for the
OL,20,Ftechnical talks and the official
OL,21,Fsigning ceremony."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
