OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,FFull details of the deal were not
OL,7,Fimmediately available, and it was
OL,8,Funclear how quickly the strait might
OL,9,Freopen to all traffic.
OL,11,FThe US previously said it would ease
OL,12,Fits blockade of Iranian ports as the
OL,13,Fstrait reopens, and would agree to
OL,14,Frelax sanctions to allow Iran to sell
OL,15,Fmore of its oil and strengthen its
OL,16,Fbattered economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
