OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,FIranian state media reported
OL,7,FPakistan's statement after a day in
OL,8,Fwhich Israel ` sidelined from the
OL,9,Fnegotiations ` attacked what it said
OL,10,Fwere Hezbollah targets in the southern
OL,11,Fsuburbs of Beirut.
OL,13,FThis attack on the Lebanese capital
OL,14,Fwhen a deal was so close to being
OL,15,Freached threatened to derail the
OL,16,Fprocess, with Iran threatening a
OL,17,Fmilitary response and President Trump
OL,18,Fcalling for restraint from both sides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
