OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781525476
OL,3,CUS-Iran peace deal 'has been reached',
OL,4,CTrump and Pakistan PM say
OL,6,FThe deal largely returns the region to
OL,7,Fa status that existed before the war,
OL,8,Fbut with thousands of people dead and
OL,9,FIran establishing a new method of
OL,10,Fnegotiating pressure with its ability
OL,11,Fto influence transits of the strait.
OL,13,FThe waterway is crucial to significant
OL,14,Fshipments of oil, natural gas and
OL,15,Frelated products like fertiliser, and
OL,16,Fits effective closure rocked the
OL,17,Fglobal economy.
OL,19,FThis is a breaking story and is being
OL,20,Fupdated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
